div1.p: Territory of Washington County of Walla Walla

I W J Tompkins to whom the within writ is directed hereby asecpts service of the - within writ and in obidince thereto have here at the time and place designated therein the odies of the said Wm Moore and JM Burks and return that I hold them prisoners by virture of authority of A. Lovon of Montane Territory commeneated to me by letter barring date August 4th 1864
